# This file ensures the logs directory is tracked by git
# while the actual log files are ignored (see .gitignore)
# 
# The logs directory is used to store:
# - Application error logs (StudentApp_*.log)
# - Migration-specific logs (migrations_*.log)
# - Exported error reports
# 
# Log files are automatically rotated when they reach 50MB
# and the system keeps the last 10 log files